text: Eugene Ambuchi Asike (born 30 November 1993) is a Kenyan international footballer who plays for Tusker, as a centre back. ==Career== Asike has played club football for Kenya Commercial Bank, Sofapaka and Tusker. He made his international debut for Kenya in 2012. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Kenyan footballers Category:Kenya international footballers Category:Kenya Commercial Bank S.C. players Category:Sofapaka F.C. players Category:Gor Mahia F.C. players Category:Kenyan Premier League players Category:Association football defenders
